    """<p class="eq-p">Position sizing is where knowledge meets adulthood. No article—especially in {cluster}—can know your cash needs, job risk, or debt obligations. Cap downside in dollars you can lose without changing your life. If that cap implies a tiny position, that is data, not failure.</p>""",
